SO much to offer, 10 foot vaulted ceilings, HUGE game/family room upstairs, arched doorways, WALK in Closets in EVERY bedroom and much more.  Easy access to Fort Sam --- Randolph Air Force Base.  Minutes away from shopping and groceries stores.
